---
title: Pan-Seared Salmon with Arugula-Mint Pesto, Quinoa Salad, and Char-Broiled Snap Peas
description: Peppery arugula and refreshing mint sub in for basil in this non-traditional pesto. It’s the perfect accompaniment to rich, flaky salmon. You’ll be shocked by how delicious sugar snap peas can be after a flash under the broiler—it’s a veggie revelation!
